---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	PURPOSE:  Get Value of KM Variable & Set to Default if it doesn't exist
	PARAMETERS:
		• pKMVarNameStr				| text	| Keyboard Maestro Variable Name
		• pDefaultValueStr		| text	| Default value if Variable doesn't exist
	RETURNS:	KM Var Value
	REQUIRES: Keyboard Maestro 8.0.3+
	AUTHOR:  JMichaelTX
	—————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————
*)	local kmVarStr, kmInst		set kmInst to system attribute "KMINSTANCE"		tell application "Keyboard Maestro Engine"		if ((pKMVarNameStr starts with "Local") or (pKMVarNameStr starts with "Instance")) then			set kmVarStr to getvariable pKMVarNameStr instance kmInst		else			set kmVarStr to getvariable pKMVarNameStr		end if	end tell	if (kmVarStr = "") then set kmVarStr to pDefaultValueStr		return kmVarStr	end getKMVar--~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ END OF handler getKMVar ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
